quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  2,158,"Mu by’ukuri, Swafa na Maruwa19ni bimwe mu bimenyetso bya Allah. Bityo uzakora umutambagiro mutagatifu wa Hija20 cyangwa Umura21 kuri iyo nzu; ntacyo bitwaye kuri we kuyitambagira yombi (iyo misozi ya Swafa na Maruwa). N’uzakora ibyiza ku bushake bwe, mu by’ukuri Allah ni Ushima, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  2,159,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bahishaibimenyetso bigaragara ndetse n’umuyoboro twahishuye, nyuma y’uko tubigaragarije abantu mu gitabo,abo Allah arabavuma ndetse n’abavuma bose bakabasabira imivumo"
  2,160,"Uretse abicujije bagakora ibikorwa byiza kandi bakagaragaza (ibyo bari barahishe); abo ni bo nakirira ukwicuza kwabo. Ni nanjye Uwakira ukwicuza,Nyirimbabazi"
  2,161,"Mu by’ukuri, abahakanye bakanapfa ari abahakanyi, abo umuvumo wa Allah ubariho, uw’Abamalayika, n’uw’abantu bose"
  2,162,"Bazawubamo ubuziraherezo, ntibazoroherezwa ibihano ndetse nta nubwo bazarindirizwa"
  2,163,"Kandi Imana yanyu ni Imana imwe, nta yindi mana ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri uretse yo, Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  2,164,"Mu by’ukuri, mu kuremwa kw’ibirere n’isi, kubisikana kw’ijoro n’amanywa, amato agenda mu nyanja mu bifitiye abantu akamaro, amazi (imvura) Allah amanura mu kirere nuko akayahesha isi ubuzima nyuma yo gupfa (gukakara) kwayo, akanayikwizamo inyamaswa z’amoko yose, n’ihindagurika ry’imiyaga n’ibicu bigenzwa hagati y’ikirere n’isi; rwose ibyo ubumwe ni ibimenyetso bw’Imana, (bigaragaza ubushobozi n’ingabire byayo) ku bantu bafite ubwenge"
  2,165,"No mu bantu hari abishyiriraho ibigirwamana mu kimbo cya Allah, bakabikunda urukundo nk’urwo bakunda Allah. Nyamara abemera bakunda Allah urukundo rukomeye. Kandi abahuguje (imitima yabo babangikanya Allah) iyo baza kumenya- ubwo bazaba babona ibihano (ku munsi w’imperuka)- ko imbaraga zose ari iza Allah, kandi ko mu by’ukuri, Allah ari Nyir’ibihano bikaze, (ntibari kubangikanya Allah)"
  2,166,"Ubwo abakurikiwe bazihakana ababakurikiye (mu kubangikanya Allah), nibamara kubona ibihano, ibyabahuzaga bizavaho"
  2,167,"Na babandi bakurikiye (ababayobeje)bazavuga bati \"Iyaba twari dufite uko twagaruka (ku isi) maze ngo tubihakane nk’uko na bo batwihakanye\". Nguko uko Allah azabereka ibikorwa byabo bibe agahinda kuri bo, kandi ntibazava mu muriro"
  2,168,"Yemwe bantu! Nimuryemu biri ku isi byaziruwe kandi byiza, ntimuzanakurikire inzira za Shitani. Mu by’ukuri, yo ni umwanzi wanyu ugaragara"
  2,169,"Mu by’ukuri, ibategeka ibibi, ibikozasoni no guhimbira Allah ibyo mutazi"
  2,170,"Niyo babwiwe bati \"Nimukurikire ibyo Allah yahishuye\", baravuga bati \"Ahubwo dukurikira ibyo twasanganye abakurambere bacu\". Ese n’ubwo abakurambere babo nta cyo baba bari bazi cyangwa bataranayobotse (bari kubakurikira)"
  2,171,"N’urugero rwa babandi bahakanye ni nk’ukabukira (inyamaswa) zitumva uretse (kumva) urusaku n’urwamo gusa. (Abo bameze) nk’abatumva, abatavugandetse n’abatabona, rwose abo nta bwenge bagira (bwo gukora ibibafitiye umumaro)"
  2,172,Yemwe abemeye! Murye mu byiza twabafunguriye kandi mushimire Allah niba koko ari we wenyine mugaragira
  2,173,"Mu by’ukuri, (Allah) yabaziririje (kurya) icyipfushije, ikiremve, inyama y’ingurube n’icyabagiwe ibitari Allah (mu mihango yibangikanyamana). Ariko uzasumbirizwa (akarya kuri ibyo) atari ukwigomeka cyangwa kurenza urugero, nta cyaha kuri we. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimbabazi"
  2,174,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bahisha ibyo Allah yahishuye mu bitabo, maze bakabigurana igiciro gito, abo nta kindi bashyira mu nda zabo usibye umuriro, kandi ku munsi wimperuka ntabwo Allah azabavugisha, nta n’ubwo azabeza (ibyaha), ndetse bazahanishwa ibihano bibabaza"
  2,175,"Abo ni bo bahisemo kuyobababisimbuza kuyoboka, n’ibihano babisimbuza kubabarirwa ibyaha. Nonese ni iki kizabashoboza kwihanganira umuriro"
  2,176,"Ibyo (bihano) ni ukubera ko Allah yahishuye ibitabo bikubiyemo ukuri (bakabihakana). Rwose abataravuze rumwe ku gitabo, bari mu mpaka n’ubushyamirane biri kure (y’ukuri)"